IN THE SUMMER.

05:43.877 --> 05:45.579
- YOU NEED
TO CALM HIM, JOHN.

05:45.613 --> 05:46.580
- I DON'T KNOW
HOW TO REACH HIM.

05:46.614 --> 05:47.815
- I'M SURE YOUR MOTHER DOES.

05:47.848 --> 05:49.417
- HOW CAN YOU HATE
YOUR OWN FATHER?

05:49.450 --> 05:50.918
- I DON'T HATE HIM.
I DON'T LOVE HIM.

05:50.951 --> 05:53.587
I HAVE NO FEELINGS FOR HIM
WHATSOEVER.

05:53.621 --> 05:54.922
- BULLSH--.
YOU TOOK ALL YOUR ANGER

05:54.955 --> 05:55.989
AND RESENTMENT FOR HIM,
AND YOU TURN 'EM

05:56.023 --> 05:57.758
INTO A MESS
OF COMMITMENT PROBLEMS

05:57.791 --> 05:59.493
THAT IS SCREWING UP YOUR DEAL
WITH THERESA.

05:59.527 --> 06:01.529
- STOP.
- THE COMPASS IN YOUR CROTCH

06:01.562 --> 06:02.730
KNOWS SHE'S THE HOTTEST CHICK
YOU'LL EVER BE WITH,

06:02.763 --> 06:04.364
BUT YOUR FEARS
ABOUT YOUR FATHER

06:04.398 --> 06:07.000
HAVE INFECTED
YOUR THICK IRISH BRAIN.

06:07.034 --> 06:08.736
FIRST TIME IN THE HISTORY
OF CIVILIZATION

06:08.769 --> 06:11.104
A MAN'S COCK IS ACTUALLY
SMARTER THAN HE IS.

06:11.138 --> 06:14.374
LOOK UP YOUR DAD,
AND FACE HOW YOU FEEL.

06:14.408 --> 06:15.275
- YOU KNOW WHAT, HANK?
YOU'RE RIGHT.

06:15.308 --> 06:16.444
YOU'RE ABSOLUTELY RIGHT.

06:16.477 --> 06:18.011
I SHOULD LOOK HIM UP,

06:18.045 --> 06:20.213
TO THANK HIM.

06:20.247 --> 06:24.885
BECAUSE HIM ABANDONING
MY MOM AND I FOR COCO,

06:24.918 --> 06:26.687
BEST THING THAT
EVER HAPPENED TO US.

06:26.720 --> 06:30.357
WE BONDED, LIKE TWO PEAS
IN A POD.

06:30.390 --> 06:31.725
I MEAN, SURE THERE
WAS SOME DOWNSIDES,

06:31.759 --> 06:33.427
LIKE I WAS NEVER ALLOWED

06:33.461 --> 06:37.297
TO HAVE COCOA PUFFS
IN THE HOUSE.

06:37.330 --> 06:40.100
BUT THAT WAS MORE
THAN MADE UP FOR

06:40.133 --> 06:42.970
BY HER TEACHING ME
HOW TO SHAVE,

06:43.003 --> 06:45.706
AND HOW TO DRIVE,

06:45.739 --> 06:46.807
AND HOW TO HIT A CURVEBALL.

06:46.840 --> 06:49.309
I MEAN, WE WERE
ALWAYS TOGETHER.

06:49.342 --> 06:50.578
DO YOU KNOW WHAT IT'S LIKE
TO HAVE YOUR MOM

06:50.611 --> 06:51.645
TAKE YOU TO A BULLS GAME?

06:51.679 --> 06:54.114
NO, YOU DON'T.

06:54.147 --> 06:56.584
