WENT TO A BEARS GAME

06:56.617 --> 06:59.553
WITH YOUR MOM, AND HAD HER
MAKE YOU WEAR MITTENS...

06:59.587 --> 07:01.822
[knocks]

07:01.855 --> 07:05.559
WHEN YOU'RE 14.

07:05.593 --> 07:07.160
I BET YOU NEVER
SAT WITH YOUR MOM

07:07.194 --> 07:09.630
AT A BLACKHAWKS GAME,
AND SAW SOME FRIENDS

07:09.663 --> 07:12.299
FROM SCHOOL WATCHING
WHILE SHE TOOK HER SALIVA

07:12.332 --> 07:14.602
AND SLICKED BACK
YOUR HAIR.

07:14.635 --> 07:16.336
ONLY YOU CAN'T
TELL HER TO STOP,

07:16.369 --> 07:17.571
'CAUSE YOU'RE AFRAID
IF YOU HURT HER FEELINGS,

07:17.605 --> 07:18.739
SHE'S GONNA
ABANDON YOU TOO.

07:18.772 --> 07:20.608
SH--. MY COCK IS SMARTER
THAN I AM.

07:20.641 --> 07:23.744
AND I GOTTA DEAL WITH
FINDING MY GODDAMN DAD.

07:23.777 --> 07:26.814
MOTHER--
[growls]

07:31.552 --> 07:32.853
- I'M TELLIN' YA,
THIS IS ALL COVERED

07:32.886 --> 07:34.822
